{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FeaturePolicy: getAllowlistForFeature() method","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FeaturePolicy/getAllowlistForFeature","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","browserCompat":["api.FeaturePolicy.getAllowlistForFeature"],"sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FeaturePolicy\"><code>FeaturePolicy</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FeaturePolicy/allowedFeatures\"><code>allowedFeatures()</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FeaturePolicy/allowsFeature\"><code>allowsFeature()</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FeaturePolicy/features\"><code>features()</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li><li><em><code>getAllowlistForFeature()</code> <abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></em></li></ol></details></li></ol>","sidebarMacro":"APIRef","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>\n  The <strong><code>getAllowlistForFeature()</code></strong>\n  method of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FeaturePolicy\"><code>FeaturePolicy</code></a> interface enables querying of the allowlist for a specific feature for the current Permissions Policy.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> allowlist <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> FeaturePolicy<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getAllowlistForFeature</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>feature<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"feature_name\">Feature name</h4>\n<p>A specific feature name must be specified.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>An array of strings containing the serialized list of allowed origins for the feature. If a wildcard (<code>*</code>) is used, the array will contain <code>*</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"errors","title":"Errors","isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The function will raise a warning if the specified Permissions Policy directive name is not\n  known. However, it will also return empty array, indicating that no origin is allowed to\n  use the feature.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The following example prints all the origins that are allowed to use Camera API by the\n  Permissions Policy. Please note that Camera API might also be restricted by the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API\">Permissions API</a>, if the user did not grant the corresponding permission.\n</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// First, get the FeaturePolicy object</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> featurePolicy <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>featurePolicy<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Query for specific feature</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> allowlist <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> featurePolicy<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getAllowlistForFeature</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"camera\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> origin <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> allowlist<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>origin<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[],"query":"api.FeaturePolicy.getAllowlistForFeature"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.FeaturePolicy.getAllowlistForFeature"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Errors","id":"errors"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The getAllowlistForFeature()\n  method of the FeaturePolicy interface enables querying of the allowlist for a specific feature for the current Permissions Policy.","popularity":0,"modified":"2023-04-26T15:24:44.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/featurepolicy/getallowlistforfeature","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/api/featurepolicy/getallowlistforfeature/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/a604faf24940b0e628532a8f5d4bb703905bb039","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"getAllowlistForFeature()","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FeaturePolicy","title":"FeaturePolicy"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FeaturePolicy/getAllowlistForFeature","title":"getAllowlistForFeature()"}],"pageTitle":"FeaturePolicy: getAllowlistForFeature() method - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}